<font color="#00ff40">♪ I could play God... ♪</font>

179
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,760
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak enak badan.</font>

180
00:10:21,828 --> 00:10:23,195
<font color="#00ff40">Boleh aku masuk ?</font>

181
00:10:29,802 --> 00:10:32,671
<font color="#00ff40">Apa ini soal sekolah ?</font>

182
00:10:32,739 --> 00:10:35,074
<font color="#00ff40">Ya. Benar.</font>

183
00:10:35,142 --> 00:10:36,976
<font color="#00ff40">Kalau kau ingin memberiku nasihat...</font>

184
00:10:37,044 --> 00:10:38,578
<font color="#00ff40">...karena menurutmu, akan
membuatmu lebih baik.</font>

185
00:10:38,645 --> 00:10:40,246
<font color="#00ff40">Mengapa aku merasa begitu ?</font>

186
00:10:40,313 --> 00:10:42,515
<font color="#00ff40">Karena... Aku tahu penting buatmu...</font>

187
00:10:42,582 --> 00:10:43,883
<font color="#00ff40">...untuk menjadi ayah yang baik.</font>

188
00:10:43,951 --> 00:10:47,755
<font color="#00ff40">Hanya kalau aku sudah jadi ayah yang baik.</font>

189
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:50,791
<font color="#00ff40">Tapi, akhir-akhir ini, aku ayah yang buruk.</font>

190
00:10:52,127 --> 00:10:53,929
<font color="#00ff40">Maafkan aku.</font>

191
00:10:53,996 --> 00:10:56,231
<font color="#00ff40">Apa itu semacam trik...</font>

192
00:10:56,299 --> 00:10:57,833
<font color="#00ff40">...untuk membuatku kasihan padamu ?</font>

193
00:10:57,901 --> 00:11:02,572
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak bisa membayangkan buatmu...</font>

194
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:04,407
<font color="#00ff40">...pindah, dan masuk sekolah baru...</font>

195
00:11:04,475 --> 00:11:07,843
<font color="#00ff40">...dan semua kegilaan yang menimpa kita di sini.</font>

196
00:11:07,911 --> 00:11:10,712
<font color="#00ff40">Hei, Ingat, Tahun lalu, saat kau bilang...</font>

197
00:11:10,780 --> 00:11:12,281
<font color="#00ff40">Kau ingin masuk Universitas Harvard ?</font>

198
00:11:12,348 --> 00:11:14,283
<font color="#00ff40">Mungkin, aku mengatakannya
untuk menyenangkanmu..</font>

199
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:16,384
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tahu..</font>

200
00:11:16,452 --> 00:11:18,954
<font color="#00ff40">Aku juga tahu, kau pintar...</font>

201
00:11:19,021 --> 00:11:21,256
<font color="#00ff40">...dan kau bisa kuliah di manapun yang kau mau.</font>

202
00:11:28,163 --> 00:11:29,863
<font color="#00ff40">Ayolah, Violet.</font>

203
00:11:29,931 --> 00:11:30,997
<font color="#00ff40">Ada apa denganmu ?</font>

204
00:11:33,234 --> 00:11:34,834
<font color="#00ff40">Ini tak seperti dirimu.</font>

205
00:11:37,538 --> 00:11:39,505
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak bisa masuk kembali, Ayah.</font>

206
00:11:39,573 --> 00:11:42,141
<font color="#00ff40">Oke, Oke, Sayang...
Oke...</font>

207
00:11:42,209 --> 00:11:43,576
<font color="#00ff40">Kita akan cari sekolah lain.</font>

208
00:11:43,644 --> 00:11:45,445
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak, Semuanya sama !</font>

209
00:11:45,512 --> 00:11:49,449
<font color="#00ff40">Sayang, Kau harus memahamiku...</font>

210
00:11:49,516 --> 00:11:52,585
<font color="#00ff40">Kita akan mencarikanmu sekolah baru...</font>

211
00:11:52,653 --> 00:11:54,720
<font color="#00ff40">...tapi kau harus masuk besok,...</font>

212
00:11:54,788 --> 00:11:56,856
<font color="#00ff40">...kalau tidak, kita akan bermasalah di pengadilan.</font>

213
00:11:58,725 --> 00:11:59,625
<font color="#00ff40">Setuju ?</font>

214
00:12:05,063 --> 00:12:07,031
<font color="#00ff40">Setuju.</font>

215
00:12:13,905 --> 00:12:14,939
<font color="#00ff40">Constance.</font>

216
00:12:15,006 --> 00:12:16,140
<font color="#00ff40">Halo, Lawrence.</font>

217
00:12:16,208 --> 00:12:18,943
<font color="#00ff40">Apa aku mengganggu ?</font>

218
00:12:19,010 --> 00:12:21,178
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak..
Uh.. Masuklah..</font>

219
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,347
<font color="#00ff40">Maaf, aku mengganggumu.</font>

220
00:12:23,415 --> 00:12:27,384
<font color="#00ff40">Aku hanya, Aku tak tahu,
ke mana harus berbagi...</font>

221
00:12:27,452 --> 00:12:31,088
<font color="#00ff40">Aku membutuhkan beberapa 'manusia hidup'...</font>

222
00:12:32,257 --> 00:12:34,191
<font color="#00ff40">...untuk berhubungan, kurasa.</font>

223
00:12:34,259 --> 00:12:36,059
<font color="#00ff40">Aku sangat merasa kehilangan...</font>

224
00:12:36,127 --> 00:12:39,162
<font color="#00ff40">Maksudku, Sudah berapa
banyak kisah tragis...</font>

225
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,897
<font color="#00ff40">...,sudah berapa banyak kehilangan,...</font>

226
00:12:40,965 --> 00:12:42,532
<font color="#00ff40">...yang bisa dihadapi wanita seorang diri ?</font>

227
00:12:45,569 --> 00:12:46,635
<font color="#00ff40">Travis meninggal.</font>

228
00:12:48,171 --> 00:12:50,105
<font color="#00ff40">Dibunuh.</font>

229
00:12:50,173 --> 00:12:51,206
<font color="#00ff40">Wow.</font>

230
00:12:51,273 --> 00:12:52,974
<font color="#00ff40">Wow.
Itu mengerikan.</font>

231
00:12:53,041 --> 00:12:54,108
<font color="#00ff40">Ya.</font>

232
00:12:54,176 --> 00:12:55,943
<font color="#00ff40">Dia begitu muda...</font>

233
00:12:56,011 --> 00:12:59,013
<font color="#00ff40">Dia begitu tampan.</font>

234
00:13:00,616 --> 00:13:01,716
<font color="#00ff40">Tak sepertimu !</font>

235
00:13:01,784 --> 00:13:03,886
<font color="#00ff40">Constance !
Constance !</font>

236
00:13:03,953 --> 00:13:05,254
<font color="#00ff40">Itulah, mengapa kau membunuhnya, kan ?</font>

237
00:13:05,321 --> 00:13:06,255
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak !</font>

238
00:13:06,322 --> 00:13:08,524
<font color="#00ff40">Karena, Kau tahu, aku menginginkannya,...</font>

239
00:13:08,592 --> 00:13:10,927
<font color="#00ff40">...dengan cara aku tak pernah menginginkanmu.</font>

240
00:13:10,995 --> 00:13:12,362
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak... Tidak...
Tidak... Kau salah.</font>

241
00:13:12,430 --> 00:13:15,699
<font color="#00ff40">Sekarang, Mungkin, kekuatanku sudah berkurang...</font>

242
00:13:15,767 --> 00:13:19,770
<font color="#00ff40">...untuk melihat caramu
membunuh Travisku...</font>

243
00:13:19,838 --> 00:13:23,007
<font color="#00ff40">...tapi aku masih bisa memotong...</font>

244
00:13:23,074 --> 00:13:26,010
<font color="#00ff40">...bagian tubuhmu yang lebih kecil.</font>

245
00:13:26,078 --> 00:13:28,012
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak.. Tidak.. Tidak...
Aku hanya memindahkan mayatnya !</font>

246
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,448
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak membunuhnya.
Aku bersumpah !</font>

247
00:13:30,516 --> 00:13:32,116
<font color="#00ff40">Dia pasti membuat kesal
seseorang di rumah itu !</font>

248
00:13:32,184 --> 00:13:35,420
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak tahu siapa !</font>

249
00:13:35,487 --> 00:13:38,556
<font color="#00ff40">Bahkan bisa anakmu, asal tahu.</font>

250
00:13:38,623 --> 00:13:39,924
<font color="#00ff40">Dia cukup tempramen..</font>

251
00:13:39,991 --> 00:13:41,292
<font color="#00ff40">Di rumah ?</font>

252
00:13:42,228 --> 00:13:44,028
<font color="#00ff40">Travis meninggal di rumah itu ?</font>

253
00:13:44,096 --> 00:13:45,296
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak bertanya apa-apa...</font>

254
00:13:45,364 --> 00:13:46,998
<font color="#00ff40">Aku hanya memindahkan potongan tubuhnya...</font>

255
00:13:47,066 --> 00:13:48,266
<font color="#00ff40">Aku harus menemuinya.</font>

256
00:13:48,334 --> 00:13:49,600
<font color="#00ff40">Constance, Kumohon !</font>

257
00:13:49,668 --> 00:13:51,869
<font color="#00ff40">Kumohon, Sayang. Dia telah
meninggal, dan aku di sini...</font>

258
00:13:51,937 --> 00:13:53,971
<font color="#00ff40">...dan aku masih hidup,
dan aku mencintaimu...</font>

259
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:56,274
<font color="#00ff40">Itu masalahmu.</font>

260
00:13:56,342 --> 00:13:58,310
<font color="#00ff40">Tidak, Kau juga mencintaiku.
Aku tahu itu !</font>

261
00:13:58,377 --> 00:14:01,680
<font color="#00ff40">Kau gila ?
Kau gila ?</font>

262
00:14:01,748 --> 00:14:04,550
<font color="#00ff40">Astaga, Aku tak pernah mencintaimu.</font>

263
00:14:05,786 --> 00:14:09,990
<font color="#00ff40">Aku menerimamu...
Demi keluargaku...</font>

264
00:14:10,058 --> 00:14:12,259
<font color="#00ff40">Hanya itu saja.</font>

265
00:14:12,327 --> 00:14:14,662
<font color="#00ff40">Jadi kau akan kembali ke pacarmu ?</font>

266
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:15,930
<font color="#00ff40">Pacarmu yang telah mati ?</font>

267
00:14:15,998 --> 00:14:19,434
<font color="#00ff40">Walaupun mati...</font>

268
00:14:19,501 --> 00:14:21,569
<font color="#00ff40">...walaupun dia masih muda...</font>

269
00:14:21,637 --> 00:14:23,372
<font color="#00ff40">Dia dua kali lebih jantan darimu.</font>

270
00:14:24,740 --> 00:14:26,574
<font color="#00ff40">Yah, Memang benar, untuk sekarang.</font>

271
00:14:51,631 --> 00:14:53,465
<font color="#00ff40">Shh, Shh !
Dengarkan aku ! Dengar !</font>

272
00:14:55,101 --> 00:14:56,468
<font color="#00ff40">Kau jangan marah.</font>

273
00:14:56,535 --> 00:14:57,735
<font color="#00ff40">Aku mencintaimu.</font>

274
00:14:59,304 --> 00:15:00,604
<font color="#00ff40">Mari kita menghabiskan waktu bersama.</font>

275
00:15:00,672 --> 00:15:02,840
<font color="#00ff40">Kita bisa bermain
Scrabble kalau mau.</font>

276
00:15:02,908 --> 00:15:04,275
<font color="#00ff40">Bahkan aku akan membiarkanmu menang...</font>

277
00:15:07,213 --> 00:15:09,080
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak bisa. Aku berjanji pada ayahku.</font>

278
00:15:09,148 --> 00:15:10,481
<font color="#00ff40">Pergilah besok..
Ini tak seperti...</font>

279
00:15:10,549 --> 00:15:12,150
<font color="#00ff40">...mereka harus merindukanmu satu hari lagi.</font>

280
00:15:22,696 --> 00:15:24,263
<font color="#00ff40">Ayolah, Violet.</font>

281
00:15:32,941 --> 00:15:36,576
<font color="#00ff40">Ny. Langdon, Kami punya
beberapa pertanyaan tambahan.</font>

282
00:15:36,644 --> 00:15:38,245
<font color="#00ff40">Jangan sekarang, Bukan saat yang tepat.</font>

283
00:15:38,313 --> 00:15:41,315
<font color="#00ff40">Kami bicara pada pria Korea
pemilik toko di sudut...</font>

284
00:15:41,383 --> 00:15:42,683
<font color="#00ff40">Dia mengenal pacar anda...</font>

285
00:15:42,751 --> 00:15:44,652
<font color="#00ff40">...dan semua pertengkaran kalian.</font>

286
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,754
<font color="#00ff40">Orang Korea itu penuh
dengan kecurigaan...</font>

287
00:15:46,822 --> 00:15:47,955
<font color="#00ff40">...sejak kejadian Bom di Hiroshima.</font>

288
00:15:52,194 --> 00:15:53,761
<font color="#00ff40">Itu sebuah senjata yang tersembunyi.</font>

289
00:15:53,829 --> 00:15:55,296
<font color="#00ff40">Mengapa kau membawanya ?</font>

290
00:15:55,364 --> 00:15:59,434
<font color="#00ff40">Mungkin, Karena kau punya alasan...</font>

291
00:15:59,501 --> 00:16:01,069
<font color="#00ff40">...mengunjungi wilayah rentan di kota ini ?</font>

292
00:16:01,137 --> 00:16:03,037
<font color="#00ff40">Mengapa anda tak ikut kami...</font>

293
00:16:03,105 --> 00:16:04,706
<font color="#00ff40">...ke kantor polisi, Ny. Langdon ?</font>

294
00:16:12,530 --> 00:16:13,830
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tahu...</font>

295
00:16:13,898 --> 00:16:15,316
<font color="#00ff40">Seperti yang kukatakan ?</font>

296
00:16:15,436 --> 00:16:16,206
<font color="#00ff40">Semua rumah-rumah tua,...</font>

297
00:16:16,326 --> 00:16:18,769
<font color="#00ff40">...mereka punya lubang bawah tanah.</font>

298
00:16:18,837 --> 00:16:21,872
<font color="#00ff40">Seperti kumpulan dari serangga...</font>

299
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:24,074
<font color="#00ff40">Kalau kau mengikutinya...</font>

300
00:16:24,142 --> 00:16:26,143
<font color="#00ff40">...kau akan menemukan sumbernya.</font>

301
00:16:27,412 --> 00:16:30,547
<font color="#00ff40">Bagus, Banyak uang terkuras...</font>

302
00:16:30,615 --> 00:16:32,482
<font color="#00ff40">...di rumah ini yang tak mampu kubayar.</font>

303
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:35,252
<font color="#00ff40">Jadi, Kau bisa melakukannya ? /
Kau beruntung, Tn. Harmon.</font>

304
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,087
<font color="#00ff40">Yang terakhir itu mengangkatku...</font>

305
00:16:37,155 --> 00:16:39,023
<font color="#00ff40">...jadi aku mendapat kartu jaminan.</font>

306
00:16:39,091 --> 00:16:41,392
<font color="#00ff40">Dan apa tingkatanmu ?</font>

307
00:16:41,460 --> 00:16:43,728
<font color="#00ff40">Aku harus ke bawah sana, sebelum aku...</font>

308
00:16:43,796 --> 00:16:44,963
<font color="#00ff40">...memberikanmu perkiraan.</font>

309
00:16:45,031 --> 00:16:46,965
<font color="#00ff40">Tapi bisa kuberitahu...</font>

310
00:16:47,033 --> 00:16:50,903
<font color="#00ff40">...demi uang, aku yang terbaik di pasaran.</font>

311
00:16:50,971 --> 00:16:52,672
<font color="#00ff40">Oke, Phil, Lihatlah...</font>

312
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,774
<font color="#00ff40">Beri aku perkiraan...</font>

313
00:16:54,842 --> 00:16:56,009
<font color="#00ff40"><i>Ini sebuah aib.</i></font>

314
00:16:56,076 --> 00:17:01,614
<font color="#00ff40">Kalian berdua bodoh...</font>

315
00:17:01,681 --> 00:17:03,115
<font color="#00ff40">...karena melecehkan...</font>

316
00:17:03,182 --> 00:17:06,985
<font color="#00ff40">...orang di Kota Malaikat...</font>

317
00:17:07,053 --> 00:17:11,924
<font color="#00ff40">...yang tak hanya tak punya
keterkaitan dengan kejahatan ini...</font>

318
00:17:11,991 --> 00:17:14,493
<font color="#00ff40">...tapi menjadi korban.</font>

319
00:17:14,561 --> 00:17:19,164
<font color="#00ff40">Kau merusak keadaan berduka-ku...</font>

320
00:17:19,232 --> 00:17:21,866
<font color="#00ff40">...dimulai dari kematian putriku...</font>

321
00:17:21,934 --> 00:17:23,501
<font color="#00ff40">Dan sekarang Travis.</font>

322
00:17:23,569 --> 00:17:25,103
<font color="#00ff40">Itu benar. Kau sudah cukup banyak dikelilingi...</font>

323
00:17:25,170 --> 00:17:28,306
<font color="#00ff40">...banyak kejadian tragis.</font>

324
00:17:28,374 --> 00:17:30,308
<font color="#00ff40">Banyak orang meninggal di sekelilingmu.</font>

325
00:17:30,375 --> 00:17:32,944
<font color="#00ff40">Mari lihat, Ada anakmu dulu...</font>

326
00:17:33,012 --> 00:17:34,145
<font color="#00ff40">Beau, kan ?</font>

327
00:17:34,213 --> 00:17:36,381
<font color="#00ff40">Waktu meninggal, Berapa umurnya ?</font>

328
00:17:36,449 --> 00:17:40,619
<font color="#00ff40">Beauregard adalah anak pada umumnya.</font>

329
00:17:40,687 --> 00:17:42,621
<font color="#00ff40">Terlalu cepat dipanggil.</font>

330
00:17:42,689 --> 00:17:45,458
<font color="#00ff40">Keluhan karena keributan
dari tetangga...</font>

331
00:17:47,695 --> 00:17:50,364
<font color="#00ff40">Dia anak periang...</font>

332
00:17:50,431 --> 00:17:51,532
<font color="#00ff40">...penuh dengan kesenangan.</font>

333
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:54,969
<font color="#00ff40">Sampai dia meninggal karena "penyebab alamiah"...</font>

334
00:17:55,037 --> 00:17:57,204
<font color="#00ff40">Lalu ada Tate, seperti yang
diketahui, Pembunuh massal...</font>

335
00:17:57,272 --> 00:17:59,940
<font color="#00ff40">Aku takkan duduk di sini...</font>

336
00:18:00,008 --> 00:18:04,877
<font color="#00ff40">...dan mendengar siksaan masa laluku.</font>

337
00:18:04,945 --> 00:18:08,147
<font color="#00ff40">Aku telah cukup berduka...</font>

338
00:18:08,215 --> 00:18:13,251
<font color="#00ff40">Kebanyakan orang hancur saat menerima
kematian anak-anak mereka...</font>

339
00:18:13,319 --> 00:18:15,987
<font color="#00ff40">...tapi diriku tak menerima itu.</font>

340
00:18:16,055 --> 00:18:17,189
<font color="#00ff40">Kau benar.</font>

341
00:18:17,257 --> 00:18:18,791
<font color="#00ff40">Jangan bicara soal yang telah meninggal...</font>

342
00:18:18,859 --> 00:18:21,427
<font color="#00ff40">Mari bicara soal orang yang hilang.</font>

343
00:18:21,495 --> 00:18:25,465
<font color="#00ff40">Suamimu, Hugo, dan
Pembantumu, Moira...</font>

344
00:18:25,533 --> 00:18:27,067
<font color="#00ff40">Mereka menghilang pada tahun 1983 ?</font>

345
00:18:27,135 --> 00:18:29,403
<font color="#00ff40">Suamiku berselingkuh, Itu benar.</font>

346
00:18:31,072 --> 00:18:35,610
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak mengerti, apa
yang dia lihat dalam dirinya.</font>

347
00:18:35,678 --> 00:18:40,881
<font color="#00ff40">Mungkin ketertarikannya...</font>

348
00:18:40,949 --> 00:18:44,051
<font color="#00ff40">Kudengar ada benih-benih cinta...</font>

349
00:18:44,118 --> 00:18:46,520
<font color="#00ff40">...di Brazil dekat khatulistiwa.</font>

350
00:18:51,392 --> 00:18:53,393
<font color="#00ff40">Tapi aku tak mencari mereka...</font>

351
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:56,262
<font color="#00ff40">Aku tak ingin berada di antara cinta sejati.</font>

352
00:18:59,767 --> 00:19:03,871
<font color="#00ff40">Tapi apa hubungan kedua orang itu...</font>

353
00:19:03,938 --> 00:19:06,106
<font color="#00ff40">...dengan pembunuhan Travis ?</font>

354
00:19:06,174 --> 00:19:07,508
<font color="#00ff40">Itulah masalahnya.</font>

355
00:19:07,576 --> 00:19:10,879
<font color="#00ff40">Pada tahun 1983, Tak ada
yang berpikir...</font>

356
00:19:10,946 --> 00:19:12,848
