588
00:34:57,270 --> 00:35:00,005
<font color="#00ff40">Kucoba agar kau memuntahkannya !</font>

589
00:35:00,073 --> 00:35:02,941
<font color="#00ff40">Kau memuntahkan beberapa pil...</font>

590
00:35:03,009 --> 00:35:04,743
<font color="#00ff40">Tak cukup.</font>

591
00:35:06,246 --> 00:35:08,213
<font color="#00ff40">Kau minum terlalu banyak, Violet.</font>

592
00:35:11,317 --> 00:35:13,118
<font color="#00ff40">Kau meninggal sambil menangis.</font>

593
00:35:15,622 --> 00:35:17,189
<font color="#00ff40">Aku memegangmu.</font>

594
00:35:17,257 --> 00:35:18,557
<font color="#00ff40">Kau aman.</font>

595
00:35:18,625 --> 00:35:22,561
<font color="#00ff40">Kau meninggal...</font>

596
