00:35:43,984 --> 00:35:46,886
<font color="#00ff40">...denganku...</font>

602
00:35:46,954 --> 00:35:49,856
<font color="#00ff40">Kau takkan terlalu sedih..</font>

603
00:35:49,924 --> 00:35:52,993
<font color="#00ff40">Aku hanya tak ingin kau melihat ini.</font>

604
00:35:53,061 --> 00:35:55,862
<font color="#00ff40">Maafkan aku, Violet...</font>

605
00:36:04,673 --> 00:36:06,674
<font color="#00ff40">Detektif, Kuberitahu, Klienku di sini...</font>

606
00:36:06,742 --> 00:36:08,976
<font color="#00ff40">...atas keinginannya sendiri,
